# ==========================================
# 第三步：脚本净化 (引用成熟源)
# ==========================================
# 1. 开屏广告：使用 zmqcherish 的脚本 (稳定，闪屏处理得最好) [cite: 6]
^https?:\/\/(sdk|wb)app\.uve\.weibo\.com(/interface/sdk/sdkad.php|/wbapplua/wbpullad.lua) url script-response-body https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zmqcherish/proxy-script/main/weibo_launch.js

# 2. 内容净化：使用 fmz200 的脚本 (功能最全，去除信息流广告、推广、博主好物等) [cite: 6, 8]
# 这是一个聚合正则，匹配所有需要处理的微博API，直接交给 fmz200 处理
^https?:\/\/m?api\.weibo\.c(n|om)/2/(cardlist|searchall|page|flowpage|messageflow|statuses/(unread_)?friends(/|_)timeline|groups/timeline|statuses/(container_timeline|container_timeline_hot|unread_hot_timeline|extend|video_mixtimeline|repost_timeline|container_timeline_topic|container_timeline_topicpage)|profile/(me|container_timeline)|video/(community_tab|remind_info|tiny_stream_video_list)|comments/(build_comments|mix_comments)|container/get_item|search/(finder|container_timeline|container_discover)) url script-response-body https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fmz200/wool_scripts/main/Scripts/weibo/weibo_main.js

# 3. 微博会员图标解锁 (可选，fmz200) [cite: 9]
^https?:\/\/new\.vip\.weibo\.c(n|om)/aj/appicon/list url script-response-body https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fmz200/wool_scripts/main/Scripts/weibo/weibo_vip.js

